name: GlitchedTemploSanDiegoComp
description:
Glitched compilation of different edits from one same photograph taken on 08/26/21 14:59hrs on downtown Guanajuato, Guanajuato; edits made on 09/10/21 within 21:54hrs and 22:04hrs. 

+ Following the same process of taking into account all the "parts" that were part of a search for something appealing i have included 8 images on a video-compilation, 7 produced during the exploration of this photograph that in the moment i felt "werent enough" to share, and the original the photograph itself; then re-glitched the video-compilation and this is 1 of 3 pieces produced while exploring the video-compilation. The decision of choosing this final re-work from 3 options that i made, helped me realize that i had fallen into the same area i wanted to avoid for i had made the compilation to not exclude "parts" of my process and out of respect for the pieces that build the way to a "final piece" but then again while re-working the compilation i ended up making  more than 1 option and choosing 1 out of 3, so... the minting and sharing of the video compilation is in a way a contradiction of the purpose of the comp itself, for it is a selection of a piece from a number of parts of a process but at the same time its a project that includes other "parts" of a creative exploration to be in essence taken into consideration. So it is and it is not what it was supposed to be?

                                                          here it is.
